WEBVTT

00:00:07.725 --> 00:00:11.711
笙ｪI found a faint light
in the fading dusk笙ｪ

00:00:11.712 --> 00:00:15.311
笙ｪAnd met your steady gaze笙ｪ

00:00:15.312 --> 00:00:24.132
笙ｪOne knowing glance,
and side by side we walk on笙ｪ

00:00:24.575 --> 00:00:27.061
笙ｪLonging finds no place to rest笙ｪ

00:00:27.062 --> 00:00:29.211
笙ｪThrough drifting wind and rain笙ｪ

00:00:29.212 --> 00:00:32.699
笙ｪYou are the prayer within my hands笙ｪ

00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:40.324
笙ｪA single second frozen,
tears in focus, my heart already knows笙ｪ

00:00:40.325 --> 00:00:42.786
笙ｪWe made a promise long ago笙ｪ

00:00:42.787 --> 00:00:44.786
笙ｪFor all our days to come笙ｪ

00:00:44.787 --> 00:00:48.449
笙ｪYou are the fate I cannot outrun笙ｪ

00:00:48.450 --> 00:00:53.836
笙ｪHow much must I let go
to trade for one moment?笙ｪ

00:00:53.837 --> 00:00:56.457
笙ｪHolding you close笙ｪ

00:00:56.637 --> 00:00:58.874
笙ｪWould that be enough?笙ｪ

00:00:58.875 --> 00:00:59.739
=Echoes of Love=

00:00:59.740 --> 00:01:01.499
(Adapted from the signed screenplay
Echoes of Love on Migu Reading)

00:01:01.500 --> 00:01:03.459
=Episode 21=

00:01:03.460 --> 00:01:06.019
Gu Chengye, hand over the Jade Ruyi.

00:01:06.020 --> 00:01:07.459
Then, I will let her go.

00:01:10.037 --> 00:01:12.678
Let her go first,
then I'll give it to you.

00:01:14.580 --> 00:01:17.060
You are in no position
to negotiate with me.

00:01:17.180 --> 00:01:19.140
I can just take it myself.

00:01:21.139 --> 00:01:23.698
Gu Chengye has broken
into the imperial palace armed.

00:01:23.699 --> 00:01:25.370
He intends to rebel.

00:01:26.259 --> 00:01:27.420
Seize him!

00:02:02.380 --> 00:02:03.539
Song Zhiyun,

00:02:03.940 --> 00:02:05.379
open your eyes wide

00:02:05.380 --> 00:02:06.539
and watch closely

00:02:07.259 --> 00:02:08.500
how your lover

00:02:09.180 --> 00:02:12.740
fights to the death for your sake.

00:02:22.700 --> 00:02:24.659
No! Gu Chengye!

00:03:06.339 --> 00:03:08.740
Gu Chengye, how are you?

00:03:09.137 --> 00:03:10.532
Song Zhiyun...

00:03:10.900 --> 00:03:13.500
Don't be afraid. I'm here.

00:03:13.779 --> 00:03:15.098
What are you doing here?

00:03:15.099 --> 00:03:16.819
Who told you to come here and die?

00:03:19.099 --> 00:03:21.099
From the highest heavens
to the deepest underworld,

00:03:21.580 --> 00:03:23.099
no matter when it is,

00:03:25.539 --> 00:03:27.580
I will never leave you alone.

00:03:30.580 --> 00:03:31.659
Good.

00:03:32.700 --> 00:03:34.379
If we live, we live together.

00:03:34.937 --> 00:03:37.020
If we die, we die together.

00:03:37.580 --> 00:03:41.780
What a truly touching pair of lovers.

00:03:43.539 --> 00:03:45.419
Since that's the case,

00:03:45.539 --> 00:03:48.340
I will send you both
to the afterlife now.

00:03:48.460 --> 00:03:49.545
Attack!

00:04:04.300 --> 00:04:07.060
Boss, the trouble at the gate
has been dealt with.

00:04:07.200 --> 00:04:08.497
Take Sister-in-law and retreat.

00:04:08.612 --> 00:04:09.435
As for the rest,

00:04:09.819 --> 00:04:10.979
leave it to me.

00:04:15.580 --> 00:04:16.780
Go.

00:04:22.687 --> 00:04:23.887
Let's go.

00:04:24.099 --> 00:04:25.619
Don't let them escape.

00:04:25.620 --> 00:04:26.979
After them!

00:06:23.979 --> 00:06:25.659
You can't even hold your sword.

00:06:26.859 --> 00:06:29.020
Don't tell people
you're one of mine from now on.

00:06:31.300 --> 00:06:32.580
Boss...

00:06:33.419 --> 00:06:35.179
This time, my sword

00:06:36.339 --> 00:06:38.220
won't fall again.

00:06:56.739 --> 00:06:57.900
Gu Chengye,

00:06:58.580 --> 00:06:59.900
how are you?

00:07:07.339 --> 00:07:09.099
You can't just abandon me like this.

00:07:17.739 --> 00:07:19.380
How are you feeling?

00:07:29.460 --> 00:07:30.580
This is...

00:07:31.380 --> 00:07:32.900
Didn't you say

00:07:33.820 --> 00:07:36.220
you wanted
a traditional proposal from me?

00:07:36.979 --> 00:07:39.419
After that night we spent together,

00:07:40.099 --> 00:07:41.682
I weighed every word

00:07:42.339 --> 00:07:44.059
and wrote this for a long time.

00:07:52.900 --> 00:07:54.140
Fortunately,

00:07:55.060 --> 00:07:56.619
it's not too late.

00:07:57.299 --> 00:07:58.699
I thought

00:07:58.700 --> 00:08:00.859
I'd never have
the chance to give it to you.

00:08:13.179 --> 00:08:15.380
(I, Gu Chengye,
second son of the Gu family,)

00:08:15.739 --> 00:08:17.800
(respectfully inform
the gods of heaven and earth,)

00:08:18.060 --> 00:08:19.979
(and I declare Song Zhiyun)

00:08:20.460 --> 00:08:22.380
(that she is where my heart resides)

00:08:22.700 --> 00:08:24.460
(and also what my life depends on.)

00:08:25.412 --> 00:08:27.145
(With the sincerity of this life,)

00:08:27.460 --> 00:08:29.539
(I wish to take Song Zhiyun as my wife.)

00:08:30.362 --> 00:08:32.099
(I shall respect her,)

00:08:32.300 --> 00:08:34.739
(love her, and protect her.)

00:08:35.380 --> 00:08:36.899
(For all my life,)

00:08:37.212 --> 00:08:38.779
(never to part.)

00:08:39.380 --> 00:08:40.660
(My lifelong ambition,)

00:08:40.900 --> 00:08:42.170
(unwavering as a rock.)

00:08:42.659 --> 00:08:43.938
(Though my hair may turn white,)

00:08:43.939 --> 00:08:45.700
(my heart remains true.)

00:08:46.087 --> 00:08:49.199
(Endless flowers and infinite moons,)

00:08:49.200 --> 00:08:50.700
(our two hearts are one.)

00:08:50.825 --> 00:08:53.270
(Bitterness ends
and sweetness will surely come.)

00:08:53.939 --> 00:08:56.979
(I wish to grow old together
with my beloved.)

00:08:57.387 --> 00:09:00.700
(Respectfully, Gu Chengye.)

00:09:01.462 --> 00:09:07.920
笙ｪBeaded curtains divide love
and hate at either end笙ｪ

00:09:08.225 --> 00:09:09.086
Gu Chengye.

00:09:09.087 --> 00:09:14.720
笙ｪAfter endless sorrow endured,
love is a word too hard to sever笙ｪ

00:09:15.575 --> 00:09:19.732
笙ｪPast ties fade like a dream gone cold笙ｪ

00:09:20.539 --> 00:09:21.820
Don't cry.

00:09:22.939 --> 00:09:24.460
If I cannot

00:09:24.740 --> 00:09:26.259
survive this ordeal,

00:09:26.779 --> 00:09:29.220
then burn this marriage contract.

00:09:30.112 --> 00:09:31.700
Stay far away from the capital,

00:09:33.179 --> 00:09:35.379
and live out
the rest of your life in peace.

00:09:36.225 --> 00:09:40.045
笙ｪWith blood upon my heart,
I bid love farewell笙ｪ

00:09:44.650 --> 00:09:45.907
Gu Chengye.

00:09:48.837 --> 00:09:49.956
Gu Chengye.

00:09:50.779 --> 00:09:52.099
Don't scare me.

00:09:52.539 --> 00:09:53.859
Wake up.

00:09:55.900 --> 00:09:57.779
I won't allow you to leave me.

00:09:58.659 --> 00:10:01.060
You can't just abandon me like this.

00:10:02.100 --> 00:10:03.086
Gu Chengye.

00:10:03.087 --> 00:10:04.899
笙ｪAfter endless sorrow endured笙ｪ

00:10:04.900 --> 00:10:06.379
The enemies are not yet destroyed,

00:10:06.687 --> 00:10:08.299
and the wronged souls
are not yet at peace.

00:10:09.025 --> 00:10:11.180
We still have unfinished business.

00:10:12.980 --> 00:10:14.979
Don't you dare abandon me like this.

00:10:15.500 --> 00:10:16.660
Gu Chengye.

00:10:16.687 --> 00:10:20.326
笙ｪThat year we laughed
beneath pear blossoms笙ｪ

00:10:20.327 --> 00:10:23.901
笙ｪOne night of snow
fell wild and restless笙ｪ

00:10:23.902 --> 00:10:28.859
笙ｪEvery perfect ending
hides a trace of regret笙ｪ

00:10:28.860 --> 00:10:29.979
Didn't you say

00:10:30.620 --> 00:10:31.979
that when the whistle blows,

00:10:32.980 --> 00:10:35.060
you will appear by my side

00:10:36.419 --> 00:10:37.979
and keep me safe?

00:10:38.407 --> 00:10:39.818
笙ｪWhen all fades to drifting clouds笙ｪ

00:10:39.819 --> 00:10:41.540
You have to keep your word.

00:10:42.459 --> 00:10:43.499
If I blow it,

00:10:43.900 --> 00:10:45.300
please wake up,

00:10:45.699 --> 00:10:46.379
okay?

00:10:46.380 --> 00:10:48.686
笙ｪThat year we laughed
beneath pear blossoms笙ｪ

00:10:48.687 --> 00:10:52.049
笙ｪOne night of snow
fell wild and restless笙ｪ

00:10:52.050 --> 00:10:56.178
笙ｪEvery perfect ending
hides a trace of regret笙ｪ

00:10:56.179 --> 00:10:57.300
Gu Chengye.

00:10:59.659 --> 00:11:00.932
Gu Chengye.

00:11:02.337 --> 00:11:06.586
笙ｪNo more longing will enter my dreams笙ｪ

00:11:06.587 --> 00:11:12.882
笙ｪWhen all fades to drifting clouds,
may I share lasting peace with you笙ｪ

00:11:33.100 --> 00:11:34.220
Gu Chengye.

00:11:35.419 --> 00:11:36.540
Gu Chengye.

00:11:38.260 --> 00:11:39.379
Rest assured.

00:11:39.740 --> 00:11:41.499
The enemies are not yet destroyed,

00:11:42.059 --> 00:11:43.700
and the wronged souls
are not yet at peace.

00:11:44.459 --> 00:11:46.700
Before I wipe out the Shengtang Guild,

00:11:47.299 --> 00:11:48.979
I cannot die.

00:11:49.912 --> 00:11:53.211
笙ｪBack where we once stood,
the blossoms still remain笙ｪ

00:11:53.212 --> 00:11:55.099
笙ｪThe night runs deep like watching eyes笙ｪ

00:11:55.100 --> 00:11:56.499
I will keep

00:11:57.020 --> 00:11:58.499
the marriage contract for now.

00:12:00.500 --> 00:12:02.220
When everything is over,

00:12:03.900 --> 00:12:05.300
come and marry me.

00:12:07.179 --> 00:12:09.060
I shall obey.

00:12:09.150 --> 00:12:11.211
笙ｪThrough drifting wind and rain笙ｪ

00:12:11.212 --> 00:12:14.845
笙ｪYou are the prayer within my hands笙ｪ

